name: Ozora Kendama Single Colors
description: The official wooden Kendama.  These Kendamas are the real deal originals, straight from Japan.  These are NOT the plastic knockoffs that many online stores sell.  Light, balanced, symmetrical, and highly addictive.  Hours of fun and builds amazing hand-eye coordination.  Get yours today, or give one as a gift.  Package includes an extra string and original Japanese packaging.  Choose your color below.

name: Tribute Kendama - Single Colors
description:
The Tribute represents a premium quality Kendama, combining an unmatched combination of design and playing performance.

These high quality Kendamas use only the best beech wood which is FSC certified, to ensure sustainable forestry practices.  We have improved the handle assembly to create the strongest Ken ever made.  Unlike older traditional style Kendama handles, this contemporary style does not separate during play, and simplifies the re-stringing process.  The Tribute can be re-strung between right and left handed play simply and easily without taking the handle apart.  The cup piece will never fall off like other brands.  

The Tribute Kendama uses a superior quality string, which is custom woven with high quality fibers and offers more strength and flex during play.  The handle has also been beveled to reduce friction, and eliminate the need for string guards.

The Ken is now thicker toward the middle of the handle, improving the balance and weight distribution for many technical balance tricks like lighthouse and lunars.

Every Tribute Kendama comes in professional packaging, and includes an instruction manual in English, free stickers, plus a replacement string and bead pack in the box.

Years of experience and feedback from our Pro Team has gone into developing this unique model, and we hope you enjoy it as much as we do.

name: Limited Edition 2013 Pro Models - All Cherry
description:
All cherry. All the time. These beautiful Kendamas are the hardwood version of the standard 2013 Pro Models. They are strung with the same color string as their beech wood counterpart.  The denser, harder cherry wood adds more weight to your Kendama game and has a great clack sound like no other.  The 2013 Pro Model sticky paint is a game changer, and this limited edition series is one of our favorite Kendama's we've ever produced.  These are the rarest specimens in our spirit animal series.  Be sure to swoop one before they're extinct!

A portion of every purchase goes straight to your favorite pro, helping to support future Kendama progression and growth.

options.name: Limited Edition 2013 Pro Model - Colin Sander - Frog - Green - ALL CHERRY
Limited Edition 2013 Pro Model - Zack Yourd - Wolf - Peach - ALL CHERRY
Limited Edition 2013 Pro Model - Turner Thorne - Shark - Midnight Blue - ALL CHERRY
Limited Edition 2013 Pro Model - Alex Smith - Monkey - Mellow Yellow - ALL CHERRY

name: Kendama USA 2013 Pro Models - Spirit Animal Series
description:
Our most highly anticipated model ever is now available.  

The 2013 Pro Model uses a brand new paint we have been developing for nearly 2 years, and offers a playing experience like no other.  The tama gives an unmatched level of grip during Kendama play.  

Each Pro has chosen his own unique color, and has his autograph and spirit animal engraved into the handle, so you know it's a genuine Kendama USA product.

These Pro's have spent years innovating play, teaching, promoting, and giving back to the Kendama community.  You'll be glad to know that a portion of every sale goes directly to each pro, and helps them continue to progress and push the sport even further.

Get ready to take your Kendama play to the next level.

much respect

name: Kengarden Display
description:
The Kengarden display allows you to properly present your Kendamas in your home.  What are the top 5 Kendamas in your collection?  This display makes sure they are showcased beautifully and stored securely.

The Display is constructed of North American Walnut and made in the USA.  The design follows a minimalist theory of letting the material and shape speak for itself.  The Display fits into any setting and will become a stylish element in your environment.  The stylish logo engraving on the back marks the official Kengarden seal of quality.

These beauty's were designed by Jake Wiens, a Kendama USA Pro.

The Kendamas in the photo are shown for reference only.  Kendamas are not included in the display purchase.  Mounting hardware includes 2 screws and 2 drywall anchors.

description: Smoked red oak, stylishly split.

name: KROM Deluxe - Red Oak with Marine Tama
description: The legendary wine has finally gotten a baby brother. This super luxurious kendama is crafted from the best 100% Canadian Red Oak. The high density of the red oak gives a great heavy feel to this model; a feature wanted by many advanced players. The new hand-sanding technique and oil treatment gives an amazing finish, which is shown beautifully in the woodgrain. Enjoy!

options.name: KROM Deluxe - Red Oak with Marine Tama

name: KROM Deluxe - The Don
description: Ohh.. The Don. This limited edition model is really a sight for sore eyes. The bright and clean maple on the ken and lower part of the tama has a gold like shine over it due to the new hand sanding and oiling techniques, which really brings out the character of the wood.  The walnut has gotten company from four hand painted circles around the ken which comes together as a great aesthetic look. Enjoy!

name: KROM Deluxe - Red Oak with 5mm Walnut Stripe
description: This top level burner has been pointed out as one of the best damas by most of the KROM Team. The feeling of Japanese-like kendama powers comes rushing over you as you being to jam this 8th wonder of the world. It is really something special to play. The red oak ken matches up beautifully with the red oak and walnut tama. Only 200 of these bad boys are around so don't miss your chance!

name: KROM Deluxe - Red Oak 50/50 Vertical Splits
description: Pokeballs for the win!! This series of Japanese inspired Pokeball styled kendamas are all crafted exclusively from super dense and fantastic looking Canadian Red oak. The red oak is a great hardwood in itself, but with this new hand-sanding technique and oil-treatment the finished product looks and feels amazing.

options.name: KROM Deluxe - Red Oak 50/50 Vertical Split - White and Black
KROM Deluxe - Red Oak 50/50 Vertical Split - White and UltraMarine Blue
KROM Deluxe - Red Oak 50/50 Vertical Split - White and Red

name: KROM Deluxe - Quad Split
description: The Deluxe Quad Split is one of the most exciting combinations of exotic wood within the laws of physics. Both ken and tama alike have been crafted from the most durable bright maple and warm walnut corewood. Straight of the box it is extremely beautiful as the two woodgrains compliment each others beauty so well. The precise hand-sanding and oil treatment gives it an amazing shine, which pulls you towards it over and over again. The performance is even better then the looks. It really grows on you, and after breaking it in, it becomes a machine made for all sorts of tricks.

name: KROM Deluxe - Red Oak 50/50 Horizontal Split
description: This series of kendamas are all crafted exclusively from super dense and fantastic looking Canadian Red oak. The red oak is a great hardwood in itself, but with this new hand-sanding technique and oil-treatment the finished product looks and feels amazing.

name: KROM Deluxe - 3-Spike 5-Hole
description: This one is a bit weird, but in a good way.  This particular kendama has been crafted with 3 fixed spikes for your ultimate spiking pleasure. These limited numbered pieces have been worked over by the KROM Team for a really long time, testing and experimenting with different wood typed, ken shapes and spike lengths. This walnut and clean maple version is by far the king. Spike away!

name: KROM Deluxe - 7 Layer Zebra
description: This model together with its brother (Inverted-Zebra) are two of the most beautiful kendamas the KROM Team dared imagine. The two hardwoods, walnut and maple, play together super well with a similar wood structure and density. Together they form this beast of a kendama that has a really great sound and an amazing look. The multi-split tama is great for tracking the hole when it is flying full speed through the air. Only 200 pcs have been produced with this exact setup.  Stay sharp!

name: KROM Deluxe - 7 Layer Inverted Zebra
description: This model together with its brother (Zebra) are two of the most beautiful kendamas the KROM Team dared imagine. The two hardwoods, walnut and maple, play together super well with a similar wood structure and density. Together they form this beast of a kendama that has a really great sound and an amazing look. The multi-split tama is great for tracking the hole when it is flying full speed through the air. Only 200 pcs have been produced with this exact setup.  Stay sharp!

description: This bad boy has a really special feel to it. The kendama is made solely from the highest grade of dense walnut and very clean maple. The special sanding and oil treatment does an amazing job on this model and really brings out an amazing shine throughout the kendama.

description: Don't leave home without your Kendama!  These KROM Kendama holders will carry your Kendama securely and in style, keeping you ready for a session anytime.

name: KROM Deluxe - Red Oak Wine
description:
Red Oak is high density wood. This makes a heavier Kendama which is preferred by many pro players.  In addition, the oil treatment of the ken brings out the beautiful wood grain, and looks gorgeous together with the see-through wine colored tama.

This batch is part of a special worldwide release and available for a limited time.

name: KROM Deluxe - Solid Colors - Walnut and Rubberwood
description: The KROM Deluxe walnut & rubberwood series consists of a few of the most breathtaking color options. They are of course all crafted from the highest grade of premium hardwoods for super performance and durability. The heavier corewood walnut matches the rubberwood extremely well and the two perform together like a match made in heaven. The new hand-sanding and oil treatment techniques gives these kendamas a really great feel and makes sure that even if you are not the best player in the world, this kendama is still going to get all the attention in the room.

description:
The KROM Deluxe Half Split is a beautiful Kendama made from Maple and Walnut. The ken is deep walnut wood and the tama is half maple and half walnut. The mix between these woods not only looks great, but also makes for a really nice balance between the weight of the ken and  the tama.
This batch is part of a special worldwide release and available for a limited time.

name: Tribute Kendama - Silver
description:
The first of many Metallic colors to come from Kendama USA. It sparkles, it shimmers, it shines. We highly recommend playing this bad boy outside to see all of it's glory (sunglasses also recommended) It may be silver, but this is a First Place kendama. 

Every Tribute Kendama comes in professional packaging, and includes an instruction manual in English, free stickers, plus a replacement string and bead pack in the box.

name: Tribute Specialty Kanji Kendamas
description: For all the Kendama collectors and enthusiasts out there, we're happy to release this new unique style.  The characters on the Tama spell out "Kendama" in Japanese.  3 Color options are available.  The Black Tamas are available with red or gold Kanji characters, and a golden mark on the handle.  The Natural Tama is burned directly into the wood for a classy look.

name: Tribute Kendama - Super Stick - SILK editions
description:
At Kendama USA we are continuously developing and testing new painting techniques and styles.  The Super Stick is another level of progression we are excited to offer.  The tama is much tackier than our standard competition gloss paint, making it perfect for learning high level technical tricks.  Practice on these to train your muscle memory, and take your trick vocabulary to the next level.  Each Super Stick model comes with free stickers, an instruction booklet, and an extra string and bead.

This SILK edition is an upgraded Matte version of our original Super Stick.  Being less glossy than the originals, the Silks retain the great tackiness while allowing just enough room for small adjustments during balance tricks.  The Silk editions are quickly becoming a player favorite.

name: SunRise Acrylic Tama on Walnut Ken
description:
SunRise has uncovered some amazing gems! These gorgeous acrylic tamas are strung on SunRise walnut kens. The dark wood looks great with the vibrant colors of the high quality acrylic tama, and gives an semi-transparent look unlike any other Kendama in your collection. 

Please note that this is a specialty item, and should be treated with care.  The heavier acrylic ball on a lighter walnut Ken creates a fragile combination.  While playable, these amazing models are intended to be a unique collectors item, more than a model designed for daily play and regular use.

name: SunRise Mini Hardwood Kendama - Padauk
description:
This is a special mini from SunRise that is made of from Padauk wood. Padouk is sturdy and somewhat coarse, and the natural orange hue is as hypnotizing as the wood grain!  

The mini models are 16cm tall, and a perfect size to go anywhere that you do.

name: Tribute Kendama - Mini
description:
The mini version of the Tribute Kendama. This is the first mini kendama to have the Tribute design so they are just as easy to re-string as the standard Tributes. These mini Kendamas are great for the younger players with smaller hands, or for the advanced players who want a new challenge.  

The Mini Tributes are barely 6 inches tall, and a perfect size to go anywhere that you do.

name: Tribute Kendama - Jumbo
description: The Tributes have GROWN!!!  These monsters are a full 10 inches tall, and the first of the Jumbo Kendamas to have the Tribute design so they are just as easy to re-string and play as a standard sized Tribute. Playing with a Tribute Jumbo Kendama this size brings on a whole new challenge, and is perfect for events and anybody who performs for crowds.  This is the only Jumbo that uses an extra reinforcement in the handle to ensure the cups won't slide off during the play.

name: Tribute Kendama - 5 cup
description: This is the first 5 cup model to have the Tribute design so it is just as easy to re-string as the standard Tribute. The 5 cup Tribute Kendama adds all sorts of new tricks to your Kendama vocabulary, by adding a 2nd crosspiece, or "sarado".  Another great accessory to your Kendama collection.  Both cups are anchored in securely and reinforced, so the cups will never slide off during play.

name: Tribute Kendama - NEONS
description:
Neons for eons. These additions to the Tribute family really stand out from the crowd - and your collection! The eye-popping, show-stopping Neon paint gives your dama a fluorescent flavor that is hard to miss. Grab one today!

Every Tribute Kendama comes in professional packaging, and includes an instruction manual in English, free stickers, plus a replacement string and bead pack in the box.

name: Kendama USA Classics
description:
Back to basics.  Simplicity and playability were the focus in developing the Kendama USA Classic series.  Made of birch wood, this Kendama is the lightest and softest wood in our collection.  This is the first Kendama we have manufactured using the traditional 2 piece Japanese handle and stringing assembly, instead of the "fixed" handle style of the Tribute Kendama.  A perfect choice for the player who is looking for an affordable Kendama, but isn't willing to sacrifice playability.

Please note that unlike the Tribute models, the Classics are a simplified product and do not include instructions, stickers, extra strings, or a metal reinforcement inside the handle.

description: SunRise Kendama, from Amsterdam, inspired by the TK16 Masters and crafted from beechwood.  SunRise Kendamas do not include an extra string or bead in their packages.  We only carry the new SunRise products which use a new paint formula more resistant to chipping than previous models.  Various colors for you to choose from below.

name: Replacement String and Bead Packs
description:
Although most of our Kendamas ship with an replacement string in the package, sometimes they wear out and you need extras.  When re-stringing your Kendama, it is helpful to have a little extra slack so you can tie your knot at your desired length and snip the excess.  Because of this, we include a few inches of extra length.  We also stiffen the end of all our strings.  This makes the re-stringing process easier for you while threading through the small holes.  

Our white replacement string sets come in packs of 5.

name: Individual Color Strings
description:
Replace your standard string with some flavor with these new colored strings from Kendama USA. You can mix! You can match! We triple dog dare you to mix AND match! 

Same high quality string material you know and love now available in 10 fresh color options to customize your dama setup. The ends are stiffened to make re-stringing a breeze and the result is some color steeze!

name: Ozora I love Kendama

This is a nice addition to the Ozora line.  A pearly white tama with the words I love Kendama printed, and an elegant new red and white woven string.  You already love Kendama, why not make it official!?  This Kendama comes in a clear plastic box and does not include an extra string.

Please note that the new red and white string is not as high quality as the standard Ozora string.  Because of this flaw, we are including a few free extra string and bead packs with each of these Kendamas.  We would recommend replacing the red and white decorative strings if you have any issues.

name: Ozora Rabbit Kendama

In celebration of the year of the Rabbit.  Production is limited to this year only.  The Rabbit Kendamas come in a clear box and do not include an extra string, bead, or instructions.

Ozora is an official wooden Kendama.  These Kendamas are the real deal originals, straight from Japan.  These are NOT the plastic knockoffs that many online stores sell.  Light, balanced, symmetrical, and highly addictive.  Hours of fun and builds amazing hand-eye coordination.  Get yours today, or give one as a gift.  Choose your color below.

options.name: Ozora Rabbit Kendama - Red with Gold Rabbit
Ozora Rabbit Kendama - White with Gold Rabbit

name: Ozora Emperor Kendama
description:
The Emperor is in a class of its own.  Made by Ozora, this GIANT Kendama dwarfs all others.  It's an amazing Kendama for performances and those brave enough (and strong enough) to take on this challenge.  The Emperor stands approximately 34.5 cm tall (about 13.5 inches) and weighs nearly 2 pounds.  To give some scale, see the image here.  The Kendama on the left is the standard red Ozora.  The Kendama on the right is the Taiyo Jumbo Ozora.  

Because of it's size and weight, these Kendamas are not available for children.  This is an adult size Kendama, and should be purchased only by those 18 years and older.  Because of the rarity and expense of this model, all sales are final.  The Emperor Kendama comes in it's own box and does not include and extra string, bead, or instructions.

name: Taiyo Jumbo Kendama
description:
The Taiyo Jumbo Kendama is a GIANT!  It is made by the Ozora brand and stands 24cm tall, compared to the typical 18cm JKA Kendama.  It weighs in at approximately 10.5 ounces.  The Taiyo is commonly used as a performance Kendama used often by professional jugglers and Kendama pros.  It comes in its own box and does not include an extra string.  It is available in 2 colors.    

Please choose your color below.

name: Ozora Blue Galaxy
description: Ozora releases 2 new Galaxy colors this year!!  The Galaxy Blue shimmers nicely, with all the quality Japanese craftsmanship you've come to know and love from Ozora.

name: Ozora Galaxy Green Kendama
description:
The Galaxy Green Kendama is a new color style from the Ozora brand.  A fading stripe adds a nice subtle touch.  

The Galaxy Kendama comes in a clear box and does not include an extra string, bead, or instructions.

Ozora is an official wooden Kendama.  These Kendamas are the real deal originals, straight from Japan.  These are NOT the plastic knockoffs that many online stores sell.  Light, balanced, symmetrical, and highly addictive.  Hours of fun and builds amazing hand-eye coordination.  Get yours today, or give one as a gift.

name: Ozora Pink Galaxy Kendama
description: Ozora releases 2 new Galaxy colors this year!!  The Galaxy Pink shines bright into the night, with all the quality Japanese craftsmanship you've come to know and love from Ozora.

name: Ozora Keyaki Hardwood Kendama
description: The Keyaki Kendama is a special hardwood version of Kendama made by Ozora.  This special Kendama is made from the wood of the Japanese zelkova tree, a much more durable wood than the other Ozora models.  This premium Kendama ships in a white box, and does not include a replacement string and bead.

name: Ozora Enjyu Hardwood Kendama
description: The Ozora Enjyu is a premium hardwood Kendama, made from the Japanese pagoda tree.  This is the darkest and most exclusive wood produced by the Ozora brand.  They are only produced in the unpainted form.  These elite Kendamas come in a plastic case, and do not include an extra string.

name: Ozora 5 Cup Kendamas
description:
The 5 cup Kendama adds all sorts of new tricks to your Kendama vocabulary, by adding a 2nd crosspiece, or "sarado".  Another great accessory to your Kendama collection.  Choose your color below.

*We recommend tying an extra secure knot in your 5-cup Kendama string before playing.

name: SunRise Jumbo Performer Kendamas
description: SunRise on steroids!!!  These monsters are a full 24cm tall, and the first of the Jumbo Kendamas to come in a variety of color options.  Playing with a Jumbo Performer Kendama this size brings on a whole new challenge, and is perfect for events and anybody who performs for crowds.

description:
Kendama GOLD! The Native has set a new standard with this beauty and it's only available from Kendama USA. The Gold Rush is an elegant take on the coveted color that features a semi-translucent paint. This allows you to get a unique wood-grain look with all the glimmer of an Olympic Gold Medal. Our stock market analysts say BUY! BUY! BUY!

Each custom is strung on a Tribute Kendama handle for maximum performance, and includes an extra string and bead.

name: Custom Kendamas - Energy Series
description: This series is fresh batch from our friend The Cook!  These hand painted Kendamas look straight out of a lightning storm and ready for you to unleash the energy!  Each custom is strung on a Tribute Kendama handle for maximum performance, and includes an extra string and bead.

name: Cook Customs - Gourmet Fades
description:
A new set of custom painted delicacies from the Cook!  The Gourmet Fades reveal vivid colors that are blended beautifully.  The surface is specially coated for the perfect amount of friction while you play.  Each piece is hand painted here in the USA by the Cook himself.  Choose from the silver salmon, orange sherbert, and the blue slushie.    

The Gourmet Fades are strung on a Tribute Kendama handle for maximum performance, and include an extra string and bead.

name: Cook Customs - Color Shifts
description:
The Color Shifts are back!  The Cook has added a couple tasty new colors to the table that will take your retinas for a ride.  The effect is most vivid in bright daylight as the ball moves during play.  The surface is specially coated for the ideal amount of friction while you play.  Each piece is hand painted here in the USA by the Cook himself.

The Cook Color Shifts are strung on a Tribute Kendama handle for maximum performance.  Each piece includes an extra string and bead.

Please note that the color of Kendama you receive may look slightly different than in the photographs, depending which type of light you are in, and what angle you are looking at the ball.  Our photographs are a close representation, however viewing it in person will always create a unique look, due to the nature of this painting style.  The Blue color shift is significantly darker than it appears on screen.

description: Kendama USA Posters now available to decorate your home, apartment, or dorm.  High quality 18x24 print.  Great photograph of the 1st ever Pro Model series photographed by the very talented Luke Evans.

name: Wooden Kendama Box
description: Store your Kendama in style with this beautifully crafted Japanese Kendama Box.  This box holds 2 Kendamas (not included) and is a must have for the serious Kendama enthusiast.

name: Spike!  Mastering the Kendama Book
description: Spike! is a 48 page paperback book written by "The Void" and illustrated by Donald Grant.  It is a great introduction to Kendama techniques.  It explains trick names, grips, and many of the original Japanese names for the tricks.

name: Knees - Further Adventures in Kendama
description: The sequel to "Spike", "Knees" is another great book from The Void and Donald Grant.  In this edition, they explore new ideas, techniques, sequences, and lots of new tricks.  Well illustrated, easy to follow, and a great guide for aspiring Kendama players.  64 pages will teach you how to improve your game, and of course the ultimate secret to all good Kendama play... KNEES!!!

options.name: Book - Knees - Further Adventures in Kendama

name: Click! Beyond The Valley of the kendama
description:
Void & Donald return with 3rd Kendama manual, creating a Dama Trifecta along side their two previous books. There are not only tricks aplenty, but also some viewpoints, ideas and "ways of thinking about kendama."   Includes special guest writers such as Alex Ruisch, Katsuaki Shimadera, Mr Jumpshoe, Matt Nix, and Kendama USA Pro Alex Smith.

Title: "Click! Beyond the Valley of the kendama"
Author: The Void & Donald Grant
Illustrations: Donald Grant
64 printed pages
ISBN: 9781898591238
English
